>       - ``schema_version < CURRENT_SCHEMA_VERSION``: applies the registered upgrader
>         chain; raises ``LockfileSchemaError`` if no chain exists.
>       - ``schema_version == CURRENT_SCHEMA_VERSION``: parsed and validated directly.
  
